data.description: This nearly new home boasts an open floor plan with a spacious living area, beautiful kitchen, and dining space. The white kitchen cabinets and granite countertops complement each other perfectly. With four bedrooms, including a spacious master with a walk-in closet and separate toilet room, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Additional features include a custom security door, soft water system, garage epoxy flooring, and extra outdoor slab. Fruit trees on the property provide fresh produce. Come see your new home!
